    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,400 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This example has been fastidiously maintained with recent preventative rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements, addressing the common weak points of the S65 platform. The suspension geometry remains tight, and the carbon fiber roof keeps the center of gravity low for precise turn-in. An honest, mechanically sound enthusiast car that balances raw performance with daily usability.",
